name: Snake Charmer (Harry Brock)
description:
Round up the rest of your body, and make it to the exit! Make sure you don't touch the walls!

Use A to steer to the left

Use D to steer to the right

Press R to return to the main menu!

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Only one level currently

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Known Bugs:

Body Parts won't despawn after you pick them up when you have full health
